diff:1331722454:1331722439:=3,4c3,4%0a%3c In the [[http://score.loria.fr/|SCORE]] Research Team, I focus on the evolution patterns of the (human and automated) business processes and their impact on the enterprise information systems that support cross-domain workflow sharing. Those systems are seamlessly integrated to computer-based applications used to manage internal and external resources, including tangible assets, financial resources, materials, and human resources covering all the functions and processes of an enterprise/institution. In particular, I'm interested in the '''Business Process Management (BPM)''', the '''Service Oriented Software Engineering (SOSE)''', and the '''Component Based Development (CBD)''' for an end-to-end developement approach in the context of an organization-specific virtual architecture or an extended network of connected enterprises, namely the '''Service Oriented Computing (SOC) and Cloud Computing''' architectural foundations of the '''Message Oriented Architecture (MOA)''' and '''Enterprise Service bus (ESB)'''. %0a%3c %0a---%0a> In the [[http://score.loria.fr/|SCORE]] Research Team, I focus on the evolution patterns of the (human and automated) business processes and their impact on the enterprise information systems that support cross-domain workflow sharing. Those systems are seamlessly integrated to computer-based applications used to manage internal and external resources, including tangible assets, financial resources, materials, and human resources covering all the functions and processes of an enterprise/institution. In particular, I'm interested in the '''Business Process Management (BPM)''', the '''Service Oriented Software Engineering (SOSE)''', and the '''Component Based Development (CBD)''' for an end-to-end developement approach in the context of an organization-specific virtual architecture or an extended network of connected enterprises, namely the '''Service Oriented Computing (SOC) and Cloud Computing''' archi